    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;应用商店中有&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.geekwire.com/2013/report-ios-app-store-hits-950k-apps/&quot;&gt;数百万个app&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;每部智能手机平均安装&lt;a href=&quot;http://thenextweb.com/insider/2012/05/16/nielsen-us-smartphones-have-an-average-of-41-apps-installed-up-from-32-last-year/&quot;&gt;41个app&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;
